'''Shefqet Topi''' (1934&ndash;1998) was an [[Albanians|Albanian]] [[Association football|footballer]] who played most of his professional career as a goalkeeper for [[Besa Kavajë]] football club. He was also capped with the [[Albania National Football Team]] in the early 1960s.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=21190|title=Player Database}}</ref>

